(42, 8, 28, 41, 5, 6, 8, 'What have I to do with thee, Jesus, thou Son of God most high?', 'Connection Between Demonic Encounters', 'Both passages emphasize the encounter between Jesus and a demoniac, highlighting the recognition of Jesus as ''Son of the most high God'' and the plea to not be tormented. The similar phrasing and themes illustrate the authority of Jesus over unclean spirits.', 'parallel', 0.314, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
