(42, 8, 31, 18, 2, 5, 5, 'not command them to go out', 'Request for Control Over Spirits', 'This connection highlights the theme of beings pleading for control over their fate. In Luke, the demons request not to be sent into the deep, while in Job, Satan challenges God''s authority over Job''s suffering.', 'theme', 0.314, 'medium', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
