(42, 8, 31, 50, 2, 10, 11, 'go out into the deep', 'Authority of Jesus Over Spirits', 'This connection highlights the authority of Jesus, as seen in the demons'' plea not to be sent into the deep, and the eventual recognition of His lordship by all creation in Philippians. Both passages emphasize the power of Jesus over spiritual realms and the necessity of submission to His authority.', 'theme', 0.314, 'medium', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
