(42, 8, 32, 19, 62, 11, 11, NULL, 'Power Belongs to God', 'This connection highlights the theme of divine authority. In Luke 8:32, Jesus demonstrates His power over demons by allowing them to enter the swine, while Psalms 62:11 emphasizes that power belongeth unto God.', 'theme', 0.314, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
